title: Project Animal Rescue
body: Final 201 project where we aggregated all local animal shelter animals into one place.

title: Bus Mall
body: Its the now defunct sky mall magazines that where frequently seen in planes for buses. The goal of this was basically to have a focus group make choices on what they would most likely buy and then display the data into a chart.

title: Cookie Store
body: A Seattle based cookie store. On the second page there is a function that calculates the totals and allows for new store data to be input.
